* Easy mocking of interfaces

`net.Conn` is an interface defined in the `net` package of the standard library.

    type Conn interface {
        Read(b []byte) (n int, err error)
        Write(b []byte) (n int, err error)
        Close() error
        LocalAddr() Addr
        RemoteAddr() Addr
        SetDeadline(t time.Time) error
